Finally a recognition which just screams that this is just the beginning I’m thrilled to share that our PAC Micro Finish Makeup Setting Spray has won the Editor’s Choice - Setting Spray of the Year at the Elle Beauty Awards 2024! This recognition highlights the immense love and trust our customers have shown towards this product, one of our all-time bestsellers. At PAC, our goal has always been to develop products that not only meet but exceed customer expectations, bridging the gap between market offerings and what our community truly desires. This award reinforces our commitment to quality and innovation. 

I would also like to take this moment to extend my heartfelt gratitude to my wonderful  Team, whose hard work and resourcefulness make our vision a reality. Your efforts are the backbone of our success.

A big thank you to @elleindia for this prestigious acknowledgment, and to all of our customers for your continued support. We remain committed to creating products that empower not just professional makeup artists, but everyone who enjoys the artistry of makeup — because beauty is for everyone, it’s an expression of YOU!

@paccosmetic @vaishnavijain08 #PACCosmetics #ElleBeautyAwards2024

I know it is my usual trend to make an Insta post on your birthday 🎉 
But here is a different take to it 
Each year, this day just feels like countless blessings to wish a friend first, and then a wife 
I have seen you grow not just with your age number but with an internal growth of power,confidence,boldness, and touching heights of success 

Still keeping the roots of touching countless lives with only lots of love and compassion through your teachings 

Each day around, it feels like an experience that the only and only comes with a gush of laughter, which i keep looking forward to each day 

As you step into the next year, I wish your smile widens ,you eat more outside food with me and then travel the world together.

I have a poser wife, a photogenic person , a laughing beauty, and no, i am not tired of clicking your 100000 pictures , I am ready to be your personal Assistant , your manager , your photographer your best friend just don’t make me stand in line to take your autograph ✍️ ( just like the song lyrics)
This time blessing you with some great pictures on your birthday clicked over years ❤️

Sorry, i am taken forever because i am madly in love with this lady
